snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, ‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Get ready for a multiverse-melting fan-made concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday (2026), the Marvel Studios juggernaut that's igniting the Avengers Doomsday Trailer frenzy with Doctor Doom's tyrannical takeover and reality-shattering incursions! Blasted with stunning AI visuals, thunderous symphonic scores, and edge-of-your-seat editing, this fan-made Avengers Doomsday Teaser Trailer dives deep into the chaos: Benedict Cumberbatch's Dr. Strange in a clandestine void-meeting with Tom Hiddleston's Loki, who delivers a chilling warning about Robert Downey Jr.'s rising Doctor Doom, only for the scene to shatter into horror as a black symbiote-clad Spider-Man‚Äîtwisted and menacing‚Äîstands loyally at Doom's side, fueling Avengers Doomsday Leaks storming X since the D23 drop.

In the explosive wake of Loki's timeline fractures and Deadpool's variant madness, this fan-made Avengers Doomsday 2026 Trailer erupts with Loki's urgent plea‚Äî"Doom will unravel it all"‚Äîechoing through Strange's astral projections, as Doom's masked visage (RDJ's Doctor Doom) unleashes Latverian Doombots and shadowy allies in a relentless multiversal purge, weaving the raw dread of Secret Wars into a web of betrayal and corruption. The black symbiote Spider-Man, tendrils writhing like Venom reborn, flanks Doom in throne-room scheming, hinting at a variant Peter Parker ensnared by symbiote darkness, while Strange grapples with the incursion's do-or-die mandate in a heart-wrenching portal standoff. Shocking Avengers Doomsday New Leaks tease holographic Doom armor upgrades, rift-tearing scepters, and a chilling Maestro Hulk cameo‚ÄîMark Ruffalo's gamma-raged behemoth, chained and captive in Doom's fortress‚Äîas the Avengers Doomsday First Look unveils breadcrumbs to the Battleworld apocalypse, blending fresh December 2025 intel like those Pinewood set photos of symbiote rigs and the server-crashing cast reveal livestream.

This fan-made masterpiece captures the Russo Brothers' Avengers Doomsday First Trailer vision with epic void-conjured warnings from Loki, Strange's spell-shattering dilemmas amid symbiote shadows, and wild Avengers Doomsday Teaser Leak theories like the black symbiote Spider-Man's corruption arc fueling the multiversal fire. Not the official Avengers Trailer or the hyped Avengers 5 Trailer drop rumored for holiday screenings, but a 10/10 hype bomb fusing Avengers Doomsday New Trailer buzz with bold what-ifs, such as Loki's warning sparking a Stark variant twist. id.title: Avengers: Doomsday - Trailer Pertama (2026) | Dr. Strange Bertemu Loki | Konsep AI
id.description:
Bersiaplah untuk trailer konsep buatan penggemar yang akan menghancurkan multiverse untuk Avengers: Doomsday (2026), film raksasa Marvel Studios yang memicu kegilaan trailer Avengers Doomsday dengan pengambilalihan tirani Doctor Doom dan serangan yang menghancurkan realitas! Dipenuhi dengan visual AI yang menakjubkan, musik simfoni yang menggelegar, dan penyuntingan yang menegangkan, trailer teaser Avengers Doomsday buatan penggemar ini menyelami kekacauan: Dr. Strange yang diperankan Benedict Cumberbatch dalam pertemuan rahasia di ruang hampa dengan Loki yang diperankan Tom Hiddleston, yang menyampaikan peringatan mengerikan tentang kebangkitan Doctor Doom yang diperankan Robert Downey Jr., hanya untuk adegan tersebut hancur menjadi kengerian ketika Spider-Man yang mengenakan symbiote hitam‚Äîberubah bentuk dan mengancam‚Äîberdiri setia di sisi Doom, memicu bocoran Avengers Doomsday yang membanjiri X sejak perilisan D23.

Di tengah ledakan akibat keretakan garis waktu Loki dan kegilaan varian Deadpool, trailer Avengers Doomsday 2026 buatan penggemar ini meledak dengan permohonan mendesak Loki‚Äî"Doom akan membongkar semuanya"‚Äîyang bergema melalui proyeksi astral Strange, saat wajah bertopeng Doom (Doctor Doom yang diperankan RDJ) melepaskan Doombot Latveria dan sekutu-sekutu bayangan dalam pembersihan multiversal tanpa henti, menjalin kengerian mentah Secret Wars ke dalam jaring pengkhianatan dan korupsi. Spider-Man symbiote hitam, dengan tentakel yang menggeliat seperti Venom yang terlahir kembali, mengapit Doom dalam intrik di ruang tahta, mengisyaratkan varian Peter Parker yang terjerat oleh kegelapan symbiote, sementara Strange bergulat dengan mandat hidup-mati dari invasi tersebut dalam kebuntuan portal yang menyayat hati. Bocoran mengejutkan Avengers Doomsday terbaru menampilkan peningkatan armor Doom holografik, tongkat sihir yang merobek celah dimensi, dan penampilan singkat Maestro Hulk yang mengerikan‚Äîraksasa yang diliputi amarah gamma oleh Mark Ruffalo, dirantai dan ditawan di benteng Doom‚Äîsaat cuplikan pertama Avengers Doomsday mengungkap petunjuk tentang kiamat Battleworld, memadukan informasi terbaru Desember 2025 seperti foto-foto lokasi syuting Pinewood yang menampilkan peralatan symbiote dan siaran langsung pengungkapan pemeran yang menyebabkan server crash.

Karya agung buatan penggemar ini menangkap visi Russo Bersaudara dalam Trailer Pertama Avengers Doomsday dengan peringatan epik yang diciptakan dari kekosongan oleh Loki, dilema Strange yang menghancurkan mantra di tengah bayangan symbiote, dan teori-teori liar dari bocoran teaser Avengers Doomsday seperti alur korupsi symbiote hitam Spider-Man yang memicu api multiversal. Bukan trailer resmi Avengers atau trailer Avengers 5 yang dihebohkan dan dikabarkan akan tayang saat liburan, tetapi sebuah hype bomb 10/10 yang menggabungkan desas-desus trailer baru Avengers Doomsday dengan berbagai kemungkinan yang berani, seperti peringatan Loki yang memicu twist varian Stark. Dibuat khusus untuk para superfan yang mengejar spekulasi trailer Avengers 2026, menganalisis portal kebocoran Doomsday, dan mendambakan pertarungan Strange-Loki-Doctor Doom yang meledak secara online‚Äîwaktu yang tepat setelah bisikan trailer teaser Avengers Doomsday terbaru dari acara Las Vegas Sphere.

--Berlangganan J10Effect untuk lebih banyak kekacauan multiverse MCU dan analisis Avengers Doomsday 2026!

it.title: Avengers: Doomsday - Primo trailer (2026) | Il Dr. Strange incontra Loki | Concetto di intelligen...
it.description:
Preparatevi per un trailer fan-made che scioglier√† il multiverso per Avengers: Doomsday (2026), il colosso dei Marvel Studios che sta scatenando la frenesia del trailer di Avengers: Doomsday con la tirannica presa di potere del Dottor Destino e le sue incursioni che sconvolgono la realt√†! Ricco di straordinari effetti visivi basati sull'intelligenza artificiale, fragorose colonne sonore sinfoniche e un montaggio mozzafiato, questo teaser trailer di Avengers: Doomsday, creato dai fan, si immerge nel caos pi√π totale: il Dottor Strange di Benedict Cumberbatch incontra clandestinamente Loki di Tom Hiddleston, che gli lancia un agghiacciante avvertimento sull'ascesa del Dottor Destino di Robert Downey Jr., solo per vedere la scena trasformarsi in un orrore mentre uno Spider-Man vestito da simbionte nero, contorto e minaccioso, si schiera lealmente al fianco di Destino, alimentando le indiscrezioni di Avengers: Doomsday che stanno inondando X sin dalla pubblicazione del D23.

Sulla scia esplosiva delle fratture della linea temporale di Loki e della follia variante di Deadpool, questo trailer fan-made di Avengers Doomsday 2026 esplode con l'urgente appello di Loki - "Doom risolver√† tutto" - che riecheggia attraverso le proiezioni astrali di Strange, mentre il volto mascherato di Doom (il Dottor Destino di RDJ) scatena i Doombots Latveriani e oscuri alleati in un'incessante epurazione multiversale, intrecciando il crudo terrore delle Guerre Segrete in una rete di tradimento e corruzione. Il simbionte nero Spider-Man, con i tentacoli che si contorcono come Venom rinato, affianca Doom in intrighi nella sala del trono, alludendo a una variante di Peter Parker intrappolata dall'oscurit√† del simbionte, mentre Strange si confronta con l'obbligo di vita o morte dell'incursione in uno straziante scontro nel portale. Nuove scioccanti indiscrezioni di Avengers Doomsday anticipano potenziamenti olografici per l'armatura di Doom, scettri che squarciano le fenditure e un agghiacciante cameo del Maestro Hulk ‚Äì il colosso gamma di Mark Ruffalo, incatenato e prigioniero nella fortezza di Doom ‚Äì mentre il primo sguardo ad Avengers Doomsday svela indizi sull'apocalisse di Battleworld, mescolando nuove informazioni del dicembre 2025 come le foto del set di Pinewood dei simbionti e la diretta streaming che ha mandato in crash il server per la presentazione del cast.

Questo capolavoro fan-made cattura la visione del primo trailer di Avengers Doomsday dei fratelli Russo con gli epici avvertimenti evocati dal vuoto di Loki, i dilemmi di Strange che distruggono gli incantesimi tra le ombre dei simbionti e le folli teorie trapelate dal teaser di Avengers Doomsday, come l'arco narrativo della corruzione del simbionte nero Spider-Man che alimenta il fuoco multiversale. Non il trailer ufficiale di Avengers o l'attesissimo trailer di Avengers 5 che si vocifera uscir√† durante le proiezioni natalizie, ma una bomba di hype da 10/10 che fonde il fermento per il nuovo trailer di Avengers Doomsday con audaci ipotetiche supposizioni, come l'avvertimento di Loki che innesca un colpo di scena variante di Stark. Pensato su misura per i superfan che inseguono speculazioni sul trailer di Avengers 2026, analizzano i portali di leak di Doomsday e bramano che lo scontro tra Strange, Loki e Dottor Destino esploda online: un tempismo perfetto dopo le ultime indiscrezioni sul teaser trailer di Avengers Doomsday dall'evento Las Vegas Sphere.

snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer - Reaction!
snippet.description:
#supergirl #teasertrailer #reaction #dcu #jamesgunn #millyalcock #tyronemagnus #reactions 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqdAEdkHrwo
‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, ‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: SUPERGIRL TRAILER REACTION!! DC Studios Teaser | Lobo | Woman Of Tomorrow
snippet.description:
Supergirl Trailer Breakdown: https://youtube.com/live/B06pbmJ-CAE
DCU CONTINUES!! Supergirl Trailer Reaction, Recap, Breakdown, Commentary, Analysis, Theories, & Full DCU Spoiler Review! Greg Alba, John Humphrey, and Roxy Striar dive into the brand-new Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow trailer from James Gunn‚Äôs DCU, breaking down every shot, character tease, cosmic detail, and emotional moment. We explore how Kara Zor-El / Supergirl (Milena Tscharntke) is being reimagined as a fierce, battle-worn wanderer, her bond with Krypto the Superdog, her mission of vengeance, and how this story pulls directly from the award-winning comic by Tom King & Bilquis Evely. We talk the DCU tone shift, new costume design, the sword imagery, space-western vibes, and how this version of Kara contrasts with Superman (David Corenswet) in Superman: Legacy ‚Äî plus potential ties to Brainiac, Lobo, the Czarnian Empire, The Woman of Tomorrow villain group, and DC cosmic lore.
We also cover all confirmed DCU Chapter One: Gods & Monsters projects including Superman, The Authority, Batman: The Brave and the Bold, Swamp Thing, Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow, Peacemaker Season 2, Creature Commandos, and every rumored future film (including Teen Titans, Justice League, and Lanterns). This trailer gives us massive tone, lore, and character clues, so we deep-dive into every frame while reacting to the emotional beats, the stunning cinematography, the fight choreography, alien worlds, and that needle-drop moment set to ‚ÄúCall Me‚Äù by Blondie.
Characters Mentioned:
Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, Krypto, Superman / Kal-El, Ruthye Marye Knoll, Lobo, Brainiac, The Authority, The Kents, The House of El, space pirates, mercenaries, and other cosmic DCU races teased through imagery and dialogue.
Full Trailer Reaction ‚Ä¢ DC Lore Breakdown ‚Ä¢ Comic Comparisons ‚Ä¢ DCU Universe Building ‚Ä¢ Predictions for Kara‚Äôs Future in Justice League-level crossovers.

en.title: SUPERGIRL TRAILER REACTION!! DC Studios Teaser | Lobo | Woman Of Tomorrow
en.description:
Supergirl Trailer Breakdown: https://youtube.com/live/B06pbmJ-CAE
DCU CONTINUES!! Supergirl Trailer Reaction, Recap, Breakdown, Commentary, Analysis, Theories, & Full DCU Spoiler Review! Greg Alba, John Humphrey, and Roxy Striar dive into the brand-new Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow trailer from James Gunn‚Äôs DCU, breaking down every shot, character tease, cosmic detail, and emotional moment. We explore how Kara Zor-El / Supergirl (Milena Tscharntke) is being reimagined as a fierce, battle-worn wanderer, her bond with Krypto the Superdog, her mission of vengeance, and how this story pulls directly from the award-winning comic by Tom King & Bilquis Evely. We talk the DCU tone shift, new costume design, the sword imagery, space-western vibes, and how this version of Kara contrasts with Superman (David Corenswet) in Superman: Legacy ‚Äî plus potential ties to Brainiac, Lobo, the Czarnian Empire, The Woman of Tomorrow villain group, and DC cosmic lore.
We also cover all confirmed DCU Chapter One: Gods & Monsters projects including Superman, The Authority, Batman: The Brave and the Bold, Swamp Thing, Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow, Peacemaker Season 2, Creature Commandos, and every rumored future film (including Teen Titans, Justice League, and Lanterns). This trailer gives us massive tone, lore, and character clues, so we deep-dive into every frame while reacting to the emotional beats, the stunning cinematography, the fight choreography, alien worlds, and that needle-drop moment set to ‚ÄúCall Me‚Äù by Blondie.
Characters Mentioned:
Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, Krypto, Superman / Kal-El, Ruthye Marye Knoll, Lobo, Brainiac, The Authority, The Kents, The House of El, space pirates, mercenaries, and other cosmic DCU races teased through imagery and dialogue.

snippet.title: SUPERGIRL OFFICIAL TRAILER REACTION! | DC | DCU
snippet.description:
Kristian Harloff is back with another big DC Universe reaction, and today we‚Äôre diving into the brand-new Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer REACTION! Fans have been waiting to see how James Gunn and DC Studios plan to introduce Supergirl (2025) | official teaser trailer reaction! | DCCU into the new DCU, and this first look at Milly Alcock as Kara Zor-El definitely delivers.

In this video, Kristian breaks down the Supergirl teaser trailer, talks about how Supergirl Woman of Tomorrow could reshape the DC Universe, and explores what this tone means for the future of the franchise. With connections to the broader world of DC storytelling‚Äîspanning Supergirl movie, Supergirl movie trailer, Supergirl new trailer, Supergirl movie teaser, Supergirl new movie, Supergirl DC Studios, and Supergirl first trailer‚Äîthere is a lot here to unpack.

We also discuss how this new direction fits following years of shifting continuity across the DCEU, Zack Snyder‚Äôs Justice League, the Snyder Cut, Snyderverse news, restore the Snyderverse, release the Snyder Cut, justice league snyder cut, Zack Snyder, Zack Snyder Justice League, snyderverse, zacksnydersjusticeleague, and even how films like The Flash, Aquaman, Wonder Woman, Wonder Woman 3, Gal Gadot, Ezra Miller, Darkseid, Desaad, and Steppenwolf influenced the path leading to the Gunn-led reboot.

Kristian also touches on how this trailer fits within ongoing DCU news, upcoming projects like The Batman 2, the legacy of The Batman, plus the tonal differences between past and current DC Studios leadership. Whether you're a fan of Peacemaker, HBOMax, WB, or hoping for a continuation of classic arcs from Justice League, Wonder Woman, or even The Force Awakens era of blockbuster energy‚Äîthis trailer gives us plenty to discuss.

If you're excited for the future of DC Studios Supergirl, you're in the right place.

snippet.title: Avengers Doomsday Trailer Just Leaked Early!
snippet.description:
Okay, I‚Äôm jumping straight into this ‚Äî because the Avengers Doomsday trailer is dropping in just a few hours, and the leaks we got today are unreal.
No intro, no slowdown ‚Äî let‚Äôs break everything down fast.

First, Marvel has officially added a brand-new video to their trailer playlist‚Ä¶ and yes, it‚Äôs for Avengers Doomsday. That confirms the upload is already sitting privately on their channel, waiting to go live.
On top of that, an early thumbnail for the trailer leaked ‚Äî and if you‚Äôve seen it, you know Marvel is going darker and bigger than anything since Endgame.

And here‚Äôs the part everyone keeps asking about:
Korea‚Äôs media rating board just listed the Avengers Doomsday trailer with a runtime of 1 minute and 25 seconds, featuring Pedro Pascal and Doctor Doom.
That alone confirms Marvel is teasing the Doom vs Mister Fantastic rivalry straight from the comics ‚Äî something fans have been waiting YEARS to see.

But the wildest leak today?
A short clip showing Iron Man attacking Tobey Maguire‚Äôs Spider-Man while a multiversal rift explodes behind them ‚Äî almost identical to the one from Brand New Day.
Is it real footage from the trailer? Or a crazy fan edit? Honestly‚Ä¶ it‚Äôs hard to tell. But I want to know what YOU think.

One more detail:
We won‚Äôt see Doctor Doom‚Äôs full face today, but we will see pieces of multiple new teams across different Earths ‚Äî which means the multiverse war officially begins with this teaser.

Let me know in the comments how hyped you are ‚Äî because @ChicSage is here, breaking down every leak as fast as it hits.

After James Gunn became co-CEO of DC Studios with Peter Safran, he made huge moves signaling a more exciting future for DC, which included the announcement of Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow for the DC Universe. Ever since 2013's Man of Steel, the DCEU has faced tonal and behind-the-scenes issues. Supergirl might not be the most famous DC superhero, but the character has never gotten the justice she deserves, as the 1984 movie was a critical disaster and a box office bomb (via Box Office Mojo). My snowman and me, eh
My snowman and me
Baby

Yeah, you are my home, my home for all seasons

Let's go below zero and hide from the sun

Yes, let's hit the North Pole and live happily
Please don't cry no tears now, it's Christmas, baby

[Post-Chorus]
My snowman and me, eh
My snowman and me
Baby

Dos sombras caminan sin mostrar remordimiento
Uno vende besos, otra reina sin alma
El precio del cielo se paga con calma

Lenguas de serpiente, miradas que condenan
Venden la fe por monedas que suenan
Fuego en el pecho, pero hielo en la' vena'
Jezabel y Judas, dos caras de la condena

Los veo danzar en un pacto sin pena
Jezabel y Judas, jugando con la escena

Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan
A Judas le das comida, le salva' hasta la vida
Lo visita' en la c√°rcel, despu√©s se te vira
Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan
Fatal, venenosa, manipuladora y cruel
Se mueve por las sombra', le llaman Jezabel

Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan
Qu√© mala, qu√© mala, qu√© mala, ma-ma-ma-mal√≠sima
Qu√© mala, ma-ma-ma-mal√≠sima, pero qu√© bien hace el papel de v√≠ctima
Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan (aj√°)
Aj√°, ni que a m√≠, aj√°, ni que a m√≠
Aj√°, ni que a m√≠, si yo ando con el King

¬°Ataca, Sergio!
¬°Boy, hey!

Desde el trono de marfil, con perfume de guerra
Jezabel pinta su rostro con sangre en la tierra
Mataba profetas por placer y poder
Una reina sin Dios, solo hambre de vencer

Sus labios como vino, pero veneno en la copa
Cada palabra era un lazo; cada risa, una soga
Desafi√≥ al cielo con mirada altiva
La ca√≠da fue dura, pero a√∫n sigue viva

Y en la sombra de un huerto, Judas decide
Por treinta razones que el alma no mide
Un beso en la mejilla, traici√≥n disfrazada
La cruz ya se alza, la historia marcada

Dec√≠a amar la verdad pero contaba mentira'
Cambi√≥ luz por plata, su muerte conspira
Colgado en el eco de su propia traici√≥n
Un m√°rtir sin gloria, sin redenci√≥n

Ahora bailan en llama', en un coraz√≥n fr√≠o
Dos esp√≠ritus rotos en un pacto vac√≠o
Jezabel seduce al juicio, Judas firma el final
Y el mundo los repite en un ciclo mortal

Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan
Mete pie, mete pie, pero Dios es fiel
Me desean el mal y to me sale bien
Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan
Si me tiran, si me tiran pa'l suelo
Yo me levanto con vuelo

Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan (hey)
La traici√≥n me dio la gu√≠a pa adquirir sabidur√≠a
Y aplicarla to' los d√≠as
Jezabel y Judas, sin duda, haci√©ndote el mal te ayudan
Y ardiente sigue la zarza
Y al enemigo le damos salsa

A las Jezabel se las comen viva' los perros
Y a los Judas, je, je
Los Judas se ahorcan solos
DY

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 - Bloomreaper the Invincible - Official Raid Boss Trailer
snippet.description:
Descend into a dangerous arena to take on our first Raid Boss: Bloomreaper the Invincible, available now for free for all players. üå∏‚ò†Ô∏è

Bloomreaper the Invincible is a corrupted god who lures surface dwellers into the depths of the abyss where their corpses feed its roots. This towering creep poses the ultimate challenge to any Vault Hunter, pushing your build and skills to the max. The new timed challenge system means the faster you take it down, the better the loot. Kill Bloomreaper quick enough for a chance to earn nine new Legendaries that you can farm as dedicated drops: five new pieces of gear and four new Class Mods.

To access your first Raid Boss:
üëâ you must have completed the main campaign
üëâ visit the Raid Board in any of our three faction hubs
üëâ Lvl. 50 encouraged, but not required

Check out our article for more details: https://borderlands.2k.com/borderlands-4/news/bloomreaper-raid-boss/

Buy Borderlands 4: https://borderlands.2k.com/borderlands-4/buy/

--------------------------------------------

Borderlands 4 is a mayhem-fueled looter shooter, jam-packed with billions of weapons, outrageous enemies, and intense co-op action. Explore a dangerous hidden planet Kairos as one of four new badass Vault Hunters.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer REACTION!  Too Much Guardians of the Galaxy?
snippet.description:
Thank you Helix Sleep for sponsoring! Visit https://helixsleep.com/seanchandler to take advantage of their Cyber Monday Extended Sale and get 20% Off Sitewide!

In this video, I share my honest reaction to the first Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow teaser trailer‚Äîbreaking down how it establishes Kara‚Äôs tone, attitude, and worldview, and how it positions her as both connected to and completely different from Superman. I explore the trailer‚Äôs cosmic setting, its Guardians-of-the-Galaxy style energy, Craig Gillespie‚Äôs punk-rock influence, the tease of Jason Momoa‚Äôs Lobo, and what this all suggests about where James Gunn‚Äôs DCU is heading beyond his direct creative involvement. This teaser doesn‚Äôt reveal plot, but it absolutely sets a vibe‚Äîand I unpack exactly what that means for the future of the DCU.

00:00 ‚Äî First look at the DCU beyond James Gunn
00:43 ‚Äî Initial reaction: tone, vibe, and what a teaser should do
02:43 ‚Äî How Supergirl differs from Superman (tone, worldview, themes)
06:12 ‚Äî Breaking down the humor, darkness, and emotional backstory
08:02 ‚Äî Gunn-verse comparison: Guardians energy & cosmic misfits
10:03 ‚Äî Craig Gillespie‚Äôs style influence & the punk-rock Supergirl approach
10:46 ‚Äî Lobo tease, final trailer thoughts & what this means for the DCU‚Äôs future

snippet.title: SUPERGIRL (2026) TRAILER REACTION - FREAKIN‚Äô LOBO BABY!! - DISCUSSION - DC
snippet.description:
Welcome to our reaction of Supergirl¬¥s brand new trailer! In this video we are reacting to the official teaser trailer for Supergirl (2026) ‚Äî DC Studios‚Äô bold new take on the Woman of Tomorrow! The trailer introduces Milly Alcock as Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, stepping out of Superman‚Äôs shadow and into her own cinematic spotlight. From her grittier, grounded tone to intense action glimpses, an emotional core, and even a first look at Jason Momoa‚Äôs Lobo, this teaser delivers everything fans have been waiting for.

The Supergirl teaser trailer gives fans their first official look at the upcoming standalone film starring Milly Alcock as Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, set to debut on June 26, 2026. The footage shows a more personal and raw version of Supergirl, celebrating her life and grappling with her role in a vast galaxy of threats ‚Äî a tone described as being a mix of emotional depth and cosmic adventure, similar to Guardians of the Galaxy vibes.

Also featured are early glimpses of Jason Momoa‚Äôs Lobo, an anti-hero bounty hunter, as well as other key cast members like Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, and Emily Beecham. The teaser hints at both grounded character moments and sweeping action sequences, teasing a story that‚Äôs expected to expand Supergirl‚Äôs place in the rebooted DC Universe following James Gunn‚Äôs Superman film.

#Supergirl #TheMediaKnights #Reaction #DC

Welcome to our reaction of Supergirl¬¥s brand new trailer! In this video we are reacting to the official teaser trailer for Supergirl (2026) ‚Äî DC Studios‚Äô bold new take on the Woman of Tomorrow! The trailer introduces Milly Alcock as Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, stepping out of Superman‚Äôs shadow and into her own cinematic spotlight. From her grittier, grounded tone to intense action glimpses, an emotional core, and even a first look at Jason Momoa‚Äôs Lobo, this teaser delivers everything fans have been waiting for.

The Supergirl teaser trailer gives fans their first official look at the upcoming standalone film starring Milly Alcock as Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, set to debut on June 26, 2026. The footage shows a more personal and raw version of Supergirl, celebrating her life and grappling with her role in a vast galaxy of threats ‚Äî a tone described as being a mix of emotional depth and cosmic adventure, similar to Guardians of the Galaxy vibes.

Also featured are early glimpses of Jason Momoa‚Äôs Lobo, an anti-hero bounty hunter, as well as other key cast members like Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, and Emily Beecham. The teaser hints at both grounded character moments and sweeping action sequences, teasing a story that‚Äôs expected to expand Supergirl‚Äôs place in the rebooted DC Universe following James Gunn‚Äôs Superman film.

#Supergirl #TheMediaKnights #Reaction #DC

snippet.title: The Pendragon Cycle - This Looks Interesting
snippet.description:
There's a real gap in the market for epic fantasy shows right now, and it seems like the Daily Wire of all people are trying to fill it with The Pendragon Cycle - a historical fantasy series based around Arthurian legend. Join me as I take a look at the trailer and see how it compares to other modern "classics" like The Witcher and Rings of Power.

Watch the trailer here - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RkmT-kZIHNU&t=38s

id.description:
Monster Hunter Wilds baru saja mengungkap cuplikan lengkap Pembaruan Judul 4 dan isinya sangat padat. TU4 akan dirilis pada 16 Desember untuk Eropa dan 15 Desember untuk Amerika, dengan gameplay baru Gog, kembalinya Ace Gunner Nadia, sistem peningkatan senjata Gogma Artian yang baru, dan perubahan besar untuk setiap senjata.

Kita juga mendapatkan Arch Tempered Jin Dahaad pada 24 Desember, Festival LumenHymn yang dimulai pada 19 Desember, hunter pendukung baru, set armor baru, peningkatan kualitas hidup, quest event, dan peta jalan lengkap hingga tahun 2026. Capcom akhirnya juga mengatasi peningkatan performa PC dengan peningkatan yang akan datang di TU4, Januari, dan Februari.

Buff senjata, perombakan armor, skill baru, DLC baru, dan banyak perubahan catatan patch menjadikan ini salah satu pembaruan terbesar hingga saat ini.

Wario's journey begins with a promise of vengeance against a powerful and cursed black jewel that's warped his castle and nabbed his treasure. Wario's got some mighty powerful moves, like Wild Swing-Ding and Piledriver, that aren't just good for attacking‚Äîthey're also slick at clearing path-blocking traps.

snippet.title: SUPERGIRL FIRST TRAILER REACTION AND BREAKDOWN!!! (& More News!)
snippet.description:
BIG SHOW TODAY! 

#MCU #Marvel #MarvelCinematicUniverse

Marvel fans, Kevin Feige and Marvel Studios revealed A LOT at D23 Brazil over the weekend... In this video, we're breaking EVERYTHING down! This includes some stuff Kevin Feige said that very few are talking about!

Marvel fans, we just got a few reports about Doctor Strange 3 and Blade that change EVERYTHING we thought we knew about the end of the Multiverse Saga! We're breaking down the latest news in this video!

Ever since RDJ got on stage at Comic-Con to reveal he was playing Doctor Doom, fans have wondered WHY... WE NOW HAVE THE ANSWER!!! This video explains all the evidence that is pointing to a MASSIVE TWIST about Iron Man being Victor Von Doom in the MCU's past...

Marvel fan, we have some CRAZY new reveals to discuss today!! We have production updates about Avengers Doomsday and Avengers Secret Wars! We have details about Spider-Man 4 that are interesting AND NEW DETAILS about the Battleworld Movies including Doctor Strange 3 and a SECRET MCU movie that comes out BEFORE Doomsday! Kevin Feige is cooking, and we want to update you about it all!!!

We've got new details about Kevin Feige's plan for RDJ Doctor Doom! This has to do with Avengers Doomsday, Victor and Reed Richards, AND Doctor Doom after Secret Wars!

Marvel fans, we have A TON of new MCU updates and leaks to talk about! There are updates around Doctor Strange 3, a Wanda Scarlet Witch spin off, a Silver Surfer project, AND massive leaks about a scene that sets up RDJ Doctor Doom in the MCU!!!

Marvel fans, we NEED to talk about a new Captain America Brave New World plot leak and how it sets up Kevin Feige's plan for RDJ Doctor Doom! This is really crazy!!! SPOILER WARNING!!!!

Marvel fans, we need to talk about how and insider recently revealed Kevin Feige's plan for Elizabeth Olsen as the Scarlet Witch in the MCU! This is way crazier than I thought it would be! SO MUCH WANDA IS COMING! Could this tie to RDJ Doctor Doom??? I THINK YES!!!

Marvel fans, THIS ONE IS CRAZY! We just got several reports and confirmations from insiders about the changing plot of Tom Holland's Spider-Man 4 and how that will connect to Venom The Last Dance AND KNULL!!! I can't believe they are doing this, and I honestly have some mixed feelings about it...

Marvel fans, we have some MASSIVE news about Tom Holland's Spider-Man 4! We have news of a director AND lots of leakers and insiders have chimed in on what is actually happening behind the scenes. PLUS there's some bad updates about Beyond The Spider-Verse, but I also think I know what's going on there! FULL BREAKDOWN HERE!!!

Marvel fans, we have EVEN MORE set photos from the Fantastic Four! We need to breakdown the potential leak of Frankie Raye Nova as the herald of Galactus AND we need to talk about what is going on in this scene. This was in the old plot leaks and it has to do with Franklin Richards!!!

Supergirl is an upcoming American superhero film based on the eponymous character from DC Comics. Directed by Craig Gillespie and written by Ana Nogueira, it will be the second film in the DC Universe (DCU). Milly Alcock stars as Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa. In the film, Supergirl travels across the galaxy on a murderous quest for revenge. It is produced by James Gunn and Peter Safran of DC Studios.

A film featuring Supergirl entered development as part of the DC Extended Universe (DCEU) franchise in August 2018, and the character was introduced in the 2023 film The Flash, portrayed by Sasha Calle. Plans for the standalone project were altered when Gunn and Safran became co-CEOs of DC Studios in October 2022. A new Supergirl film was announced in January 2023 as an adaptation of the 2021‚Äì22 comic book miniseries Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow by Tom King and Bilquis Evely. Nogueira was hired by November 2023; Alcock was cast in January 2024 to debut in the first DCU film, Superman (2025); and Gillespie joined that May. Filming took place from January to May 2025 at Warner Bros. Studios Leavesden and London in England, and in Scotland.

Supergirl is scheduled to be released by Warner Bros. Pictures in the United States on June 26, 2026. It will be part of the DCU's Chapter One: Gods and Monsters.

Supergirl is een aankomende Amerikaanse superheldenfilm gebaseerd op het gelijknamige personage van DC Comics. Geregisseerd door Craig Gillespie en geschreven door Ana Nogueira, wordt het de tweede film in het DC Universe (DCU). Milly Alcock speelt Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, naast Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham en Jason Momoa. In de film reist Supergirl door de Melkweg op een moorddadige wraaktocht. De film is geproduceerd door James Gunn en Peter Safran van DC Studios.

Een film met Supergirl in de hoofdrol werd in augustus 2018 ontwikkeld als onderdeel van het DC Extended Universe (DCEU) en het personage werd ge√Øntroduceerd in de film The Flash uit 2023, waarin ze werd gespeeld door Sasha Calle. De plannen voor het standalone project werden gewijzigd toen Gunn en Safran in oktober 2022 co-CEO's van DC Studios werden. In januari 2023 werd een nieuwe Supergirl-film aangekondigd als een bewerking van de stripminiserie Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow uit 2021-2022 van Tom King en Bilquis Evely. Nogueira werd in november 2023 aangesteld. Alcock werd in januari 2024 gecast voor haar debuut in de eerste DCU-film, Superman (2025); Gillespie voegde zich in mei van dat jaar bij de cast. De opnames vonden plaats van januari tot mei 2025 in de Warner Bros. Studios Leavesden en Londen in Engeland, en in Schotland.

Supergirl zal naar verwachting op 26 juni 2026 door Warner Bros. Pictures in de Verenigde Staten worden uitgebracht. De film maakt deel uit van DCU's Chapter One: Gods and Monsters.

en.description:
Let's break down that SUPERGIRL Teaser Trailer! I was lucky enough to see the trailer a few days early at a special event with the Director (Craig Gillespie), Producers James Gunn and Peter Safran as well as Kara Zoe-El/Supergirl herself Milly Alcock! But I haven't been able to talk about it until RIGHT NOW! Breaking down the Comic Book references, details and Easter Eggs as well as why I think this story is PERFECT for the DCU! Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow is one of my favorite modern comics and I can't wait for the world to experience it, and I can't wait to live it in a whole new medium from this sensational team! And now Seven Months of glorious SUPERGIRL press begins!

Will be Doing LOTS of Coverage on this one! 
Already posted a FULL Review & Breakdown of the SUPERGIRL: WOMAN OF TOMORROW Comic Series HERE:
 https://youtu.be/7ABhzgXLznI 

With a Video discussing the Trailer Event and my conversations with the team coming to this page soon!

Supergirl is an upcoming American superhero film based on the eponymous character from DC Comics. Directed by Craig Gillespie and written by Ana Nogueira, it will be the second film in the DC Universe (DCU). Milly Alcock stars as Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa. In the film, Supergirl travels across the galaxy on a murderous quest for revenge. It is produced by James Gunn and Peter Safran of DC Studios.

A film featuring Supergirl entered development as part of the DC Extended Universe (DCEU) franchise in August 2018, and the character was introduced in the 2023 film The Flash, portrayed by Sasha Calle. Plans for the standalone project were altered when Gunn and Safran became co-CEOs of DC Studios in October 2022. A new Supergirl film was announced in January 2023 as an adaptation of the 2021‚Äì22 comic book miniseries Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow by Tom King and Bilquis Evely. Nogueira was hired by November 2023; Alcock was cast in January 2024 to debut in the first DCU film, Superman (2025); and Gillespie joined that May. Filming took place from January to May 2025 at Warner Bros. Studios Leavesden and London in England, and in Scotland.

Supergirl is scheduled to be released by Warner Bros. Pictures in the United States on June 26, 2026. It will be part of the DCU's Chapter One: Gods and Monsters.

id.description:
Mari kita bedah trailer teaser SUPERGIRL! Saya cukup beruntung bisa melihat trailernya beberapa hari lebih awal di acara spesial bersama Sutradara (Craig Gillespie), Produser James Gunn dan Peter Safran, serta Kara Zoe-El/Supergirl sendiri, Milly Alcock! Tapi saya belum bisa membicarakannya sampai SEKARANG! Kita akan membahas referensi komik, detail, dan Easter Egg, serta mengapa menurut saya cerita ini SANGAT SEMPURNA untuk DCU! Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow adalah salah satu komik modern favorit saya dan saya tidak sabar menunggu dunia untuk menikmatinya, dan saya tidak sabar untuk menghidupkannya dalam media baru dari tim yang sensasional ini! Dan sekarang, tujuh bulan promosi SUPERGIRL yang gemilang dimulai!

Saya akan melakukan banyak liputan tentang ini!

Supergirl adalah film superhero Amerika yang akan datang berdasarkan karakter eponymous dari DC Comics. Disutradarai oleh Craig Gillespie dan ditulis oleh Ana Nogueira, film ini akan menjadi film kedua dalam DC Universe (DCU). Milly Alcock berperan sebagai Kara Zor-El / Supergirl, bersama Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, dan Jason Momoa. Dalam film ini, Supergirl melakukan perjalanan melintasi galaksi dalam misi balas dendam yang penuh pembunuhan. Film ini diproduksi oleh James Gunn dan Peter Safran dari DC Studios.

Sebuah film yang menampilkan Supergirl mulai dikembangkan sebagai bagian dari franchise DC Extended Universe (DCEU) pada Agustus 2018, dan karakter tersebut diperkenalkan dalam film The Flash tahun 2023, yang diperankan oleh Sasha Calle. Rencana untuk proyek mandiri tersebut diubah ketika Gunn dan Safran menjadi CEO bersama DC Studios pada Oktober 2022. Sebuah film Supergirl baru diumumkan pada Januari 2023 sebagai adaptasi dari miniseri komik Supergirl: Woman of Tomorrow tahun 2021‚Äì22 karya Tom King dan Bilquis Evely. Nogueira direkrut pada November 2023; Alcock terpilih pada Januari 2024 untuk debut di film DCU pertama, Superman (2025); dan Gillespie bergabung pada Mei tahun itu. Syuting berlangsung dari Januari hingga Mei 2025 di Warner Bros. Studios Leavesden dan London di Inggris, dan di Skotlandia.

Supergirl dijadwalkan akan dirilis oleh Warner Bros. Pictures di Amerika Serikat pada 26 Juni 2026. Film ini akan menjadi bagian dari Chapter One DCU: Gods and Monsters.

Supergirl ist ein kommender US-amerikanischer Superheldenfilm, basierend auf der gleichnamigen Figur von DC Comics. Unter der Regie von Craig Gillespie und nach einem Drehbuch von Ana Nogueira ist er der zweite Film im DC-Universum (DCU). Milly Alcock spielt Kara Zor-El/Supergirl an der Seite von Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham und Jason Momoa. Im Film reist Supergirl auf einem m√∂rderischen Rachefeldzug durch die Galaxie. Produziert wird der Film von James Gunn und Peter Safran von DC Studios.

Ein Film mit Supergirl als Teil des DC Extended Universe (DCEU) wurde im August 2018 in Entwicklung genommen. Die Figur wurde 2023 im Film ‚ÄûThe Flash‚Äú eingef√ºhrt, dargestellt von Sasha Calle. Die Pl√§ne f√ºr das Soloprojekt √§nderten sich, als Gunn und Safran im Oktober 2022 Co-CEOs von DC Studios wurden. Im Januar 2023 wurde ein neuer Supergirl-Film als Adaption der Comic-Miniserie ‚ÄûSupergirl: Woman of Tomorrow‚Äú von Tom King und Bilquis Evely (2021‚Äì22) angek√ºndigt. Nogueira wurde im November 2023 engagiert. Alcock wurde im Januar 2024 f√ºr ihr Deb√ºt im ersten DCU-Film ‚ÄûSuperman‚Äú (2025) gecastet; Gillespie stie√ü im Mai desselben Jahres dazu. Die Dreharbeiten fanden von Januar bis Mai 2025 in den Warner Bros. Studios Leavesden und London (England) sowie in Schottland statt.

‚ÄûSupergirl‚Äú soll am 26. Juni 2026 in den USA von Warner Bros. Pictures ver√∂ffentlicht werden. Der Film ist Teil des ersten DCU-Kapitels: ‚ÄûG√∂tter und Monster‚Äú.

snippet.title: Hijack ‚Äî Season 2 Official Trailer | Apple TV
snippet.description:
On this train, everyone's a suspect. Hijack Season 2 premieres January 14 on Apple TV https://apple.co/_Hijack

In the thrilling second season of ‚ÄúHijack,‚Äù a Berlin underground train and its commuters are taken hostage, while authorities scramble to save hundreds of lives. Sam Nelson (Idris Elba) is at the heart of the crisis on board, where one wrong decision could spell disaster.

Produced by 60Forty Films and Idiotlamp Productions, season two of ‚ÄúHijack‚Äù is executive produced by Jamie Laurenson, Hakan Kousetta and Tom Nash at 60Forty Films, alongside executive producers Kay and Field Smith for Idiotlamp Productions. Field Smith also serves as lead director for the series.

Season two reunites its ensemble cast of stars including Elba, who was honored with an Emmy Award nomination for his season one performance, Christine Adams, Max Beesley and Archie Panjabi, and welcomes Christian N√§the (‚ÄúBallon,‚Äù ‚ÄúSoloalbum,‚Äù ‚ÄúSchule‚Äù), Clare-Hope Ashitey (‚ÄúSeven Seconds,‚Äù ‚ÄúTop Boy,‚Äù ‚ÄúDoctor Foster‚Äù), Lisa Vicari (‚ÄúDjango,‚Äù ‚ÄúDark‚Äù), Toby Jones (‚ÄúMr Bates vs The Post Office,‚Äù ‚ÄúDetectorists,‚Äù ‚ÄúEmpire of Light‚Äù), Karima McAdams (‚ÄúDune: Prophecy,‚Äù ‚ÄúDeep State,‚Äù ‚ÄúSoulmates‚Äù) and Christiane Paul (‚ÄúCounterpart,‚Äù ‚ÄúFBI: International,‚Äù ‚ÄúParlement‚Äù).

snippet.title: Can I Beat An Impossible Game?
snippet.description:
Video games are fantastic and I love playing them but after a decade of professionally breaking them I must say they have gotten very easy. It does not help that certain publishers like ubisoft and EA seem obsessed with turning the default difficulty into a frictionless experience with incredible hand holding that removes the suspense and purpose of the game. That brings me to the focus today. A game that on the normal difficulty is an absolute walk in the park but thanks to some modifications I have made the game is now a proper stealth action fps with an experience that no other game can compete with! 

So today I am setting up an impossible challenge in a game with the most extreme permadeath difficulty I have dealt with when failure is inevitable and incredibly easy. So Can the spiffing brit beat this challenge or is it truly an impossible game!

Chapters:
02:00 - What is Going On
38:00 - The Meat and Potatos
39:40 - Outro

Brettski marched into the casino with the swagger of a man who had absolutely no idea what the night would bring‚Äîbut trusted the wheel to decide his fate. It was Wheel Wednesday, the sacred ritual of his channel, where the wildest, strangest, most unhinged viewer ideas were written down, slapped onto a neon-lit wheel, and spun like destiny itself.

Tonight, the wheel felt‚Ä¶ heavier. Almost alive. Maybe it was the way it glowed under the casino lights, or maybe it was just the adrenaline, but Brettski couldn‚Äôt shake the feeling that something was *different*. Cameras rolling, he grabbed the wheel handle, gave the audience a wink, and spun it hard.

The first pick landed on **‚ÄúPlay max bet until you win a bonus OR the machine overheats.‚Äù** Dangerous. Expensive. Perfect. Brettski dove into a Dragon Fire Deluxe machine, fingers flying, credits disappearing, and just as sparks *actually* shot out of the slot‚Äîboom. Bonus. The crowd around him erupted.

He spun the wheel again. **‚ÄúLet a stranger choose your next machine.‚Äù** A quiet old man with sunglasses appeared at his side like he‚Äôd been summoned. He pointed to a dusty, forgotten machine in the corner. ‚ÄúThat one,‚Äù he whispered. Brettski played it‚Ä¶ and hit a jackpot so big the machine froze, rebooted, and reset its graphics like it hadn‚Äôt been touched in years.

The third spin was where things went sideways.
The wheel clacked, slowed, and landed on something that shouldn‚Äôt have been there. A wedge he *didn‚Äôt* write. A wedge no one had seen before. It read:

**‚ÄúTHE FINAL GAMBLE ‚Äî FOLLOW THE MAN WITH THE SILVER CHIP.‚Äù**

As soon as he said the words out loud, a tall figure stepped into frame, tossing a reflective silver casino chip between his fingers. He nodded once‚Ä¶ and turned toward the high-limit room.

Brettski followed‚Äîcamera trembling‚Äîonly for the doors to shut behind them on their own.

And then the lights inside went out.

Instagram @ProjectSupreme ¬ª http://instagram.com/projectsupreme
Twitter @ProjectSupreme ¬ª http://twitter.com/projectsupremee

Follow Me on ROBLOX! ¬ª https://www.roblox.com/users/272629211/profile

For any business inquires or copyright concerns: Email me at ¬ª notprojectsupreme@gmail.com

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#roblox #projectsupreme

snippet.title: I Faced The WRATH OF THE GODS In Terraria
snippet.description:
Today, we face the Wrath of the Gods in Terraria Calamity Infernum for the first time. From Draedon's very own XG-07 Mars, to the Avatar of Emptiness, to at long last, the Nameless Deity. We start in a fresh world, and get to experience the void taking over our son, our entire world freezing, and the very threat of the gods looming over our heads at any given point. Can we possibly take on each of the gods and restore balance to our planet? Is there a way to save Solyn from this mess? Truly, there's only one way to find out.
Thank you all so much for watching! If you enjoyed, please be sure to drop a like and subscribe for more content like this, as well as leave a comment down in the comment section below to let me know your thoughts on this video.

#terraria #calamity #gods

en.description:
Today, we face the Wrath of the Gods in Terraria Calamity Infernum for the first time. From Draedon's very own XG-07 Mars, to the Avatar of Emptiness, to at long last, the Nameless Deity. We start in a fresh world, and get to experience the void taking over our son, our entire world freezing, and the very threat of the gods looming over our heads at any given point. Can we possibly take on each of the gods and restore balance to our planet? Is there a way to save Solyn from this mess? Truly, there's only one way to find out.
Thank you all so much for watching! If you enjoyed, please be sure to drop a like and subscribe for more content like this, as well as leave a comment down in the comment section below to let me know your thoughts on this video.

#terraria #calamity #gods
